  "description": {
    "zh": "对了，我还没告诉你，最近有一些手办流通。没有人知道是谁制作的，也不知道为什么被制作出来。我通常对这些手办不感兴趣，但我真的想要里面其中一些作品。这些是独一无二的，也许我会找到一个愿意为这些买单的收藏家。你能帮我带点这些小雕像吗？我这里有一些我不要的东西，相信你以后会用得上。",
    "en": "So, I havent told you yet but there are these collectibles going around recently. Nobody knows who made them and why they were made. I'm usually not really interested in these kinds of collectibles, but I really want these pieces.\n\nThese are one of a kind and maybe I will find a collector who is willing to pay for these. Can you bring me one of each of these figurines please? I have some other goods that I don't need, I am sure that you will need them in the future."
  },
